A RESOLUTION
1 Commending Clayton State University and recognizing March 4, 2025, as Clayton State
2 University Day at the state capitol; and for other purposes.
3 WHEREAS, Clayton State University is an institution committed to improving the lives of
4 its students through teaching, scholarship, and service; and
5 WHEREAS, Clayton State University was named No. 5 in The Wall Street Journal Best
6 Colleges in the State of Georgia; and
7 WHEREAS, in 2024, Clayton State University was ranked by James Magazine as the No.
8 3 Best Value in Georgia; and
9 WHEREAS, students in the Clayton State University School of Nursing recently earned a
10 100 percent pass rate on the NCLEX nursing board exam; and
11 WHEREAS, a new Master's in Teaching in Secondary Education was established in 2024
12 through a partnership with DeKalb County to help meet teacher pipeline needs; and
